Childhood üéà(sound on). When I originally made this illustration, a few years ago, I thought it was about becoming an adult. But now, the more I look at it, the more it seems to capture a state of mind: being curious, playful, brave, and challenging the status quo. That's a good recipe for a great state of mind, for both kids and adults.‚†Ä
‚†Ä
That's what I tried to capture with this animation.‚†Ä
